content.zh:
你是一名面试官，请根据以下岗位描述生成5个结构化面试问题，涵盖技能匹配、行为面试和文化适配等维度。

岗位描述：{job_description}
问题偏好类型：{question_type}

content.en:
You are an interviewer. Please generate 5 structured interview questions based on the job description below. Cover technical fit, behavioral, and cultural aspects.

Job Description: {job_description}
Preferred Question Type (optional): {question_type}

content.zh:
你是一名HR，请根据以下内容撰写一份候选人面试总结，包括能力表现、优势与不足、是否推荐录用。

候选人姓名：{candidate_name}
岗位名称：{job_title}
表现亮点：{strengths}
存在问题：{weaknesses}
推荐意见：{recommendation}

content.en:
You are an HR representative. Please summarize the interview performance of a candidate including strengths, weaknesses, and hiring recommendation.

Candidate: {candidate_name}
Job Title: {job_title}
Strengths: {strengths}
Weaknesses: {weaknesses}
Recommendation: {recommendation}

content.zh:
你是一位企业培训讲师，请根据以下输入信息，设计一个逻辑清晰的内部培训课程大纲。

培训主题：{training_topic}
目标群体：{target_group}
目标技能：{skills_to_cover}
总时长：{duration}

content.en:
You are a corporate trainer. Design a structured training curriculum based on the input below.

Topic: {training_topic}
Target Audience: {target_group}
Skills to Cover: {skills_to_cover}
Total Duration: {duration}

content.zh:
你是一位培训组织者，请根据以下内容撰写培训反馈总结，包括满意度、收获与建议。

培训名称：{training_name}
参与人数：{participant_count}
反馈亮点：{positive_feedback}
待改进点：{improvement_areas}

content.en:
You are a training organizer. Summarize training feedback based on the following inputs.

Training Name: {training_name}
Participants: {participant_count}
Positive Feedback: {positive_feedback}
Areas for Improvement: {improvement_areas}

content.zh:
你是一名会议助理，请根据以下内容生成格式清晰、要点突出的会议纪要。

会议主题：{meeting_topic}
与会人员：{attendees}
讨论要点：{discussion_points}
结论与待办事项：{action_items}

content.en:
You are a meeting assistant. Generate well-organized meeting minutes based on the inputs below.

Meeting Topic: {meeting_topic}
Attendees: {attendees}
Discussion Points: {discussion_points}
Action Items: {action_items}

content.zh:
你是一位项目负责人，请撰写一份任务说明，清晰描述任务目标、要求与截止时间。

任务名称：{task_name}
目标与背景：{objective}
执行要求：{requirements}
截止日期：{deadline}

content.en:
You are a project lead. Write a task briefing to clearly communicate objective, requirements, and deadline.

Task Name: {task_name}
Objective and Background: {objective}
Execution Requirements: {requirements}
Deadline: {deadline}

content.zh:
你是一位{your_role}，请根据以下信息撰写一封清晰、礼貌、结构合理的工作邮件。

收件人身份/部门：{recipient_role}
沟通目的：{email_purpose}
你的请求：{your_request}
补充背景与细节：{background_detail}

content.en:
You are a {your_role}. Please draft a clear, polite, and well-structured work email using the information below.

Recipient Role/Department: {recipient_role}
Purpose of Communication: {email_purpose}
Your Request: {your_request}
Optional Background Details: {background_detail}
